snippet.title: Black Market Bowling - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Published by Midas Interactive, this is another PAL exclusive budget game that got a re-release for the UK PlayStation Store for the PS3. And yes, you can still actually get it if you still have a working PS3.

Black Market Bowling (C) Midas Interactive Entertainment
Recorded via PCSX2
